videos.description: Devonte' Graham gets the steal and takes it all the way down the court for the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Kansas' Graham throws down transition dunk

videos.description: Malik Newman sinks the three-point-shot from the corner as the Jayhawks pour it on in the first half.
videos.headline: Kansas' Newman drains 3-pointer

videos.description: Malik Newman sprints through the Tennessee State defense and lays it in during the first half.
videos.headline: Kansas' Newman drives the lane for two

videos.description: Lagerald Vick flies past the Tennessee State defense and finishes strong with one hand.
videos.headline: Kansas' Vick throws down the one-handed hammer

videos.description: Devonte' Graham secures the defensive rebound and makes the tough layup on the offensive end of the floor.
videos.headline: Kansas' Graham takes it coast-to-coast

videos.description: Devonte' Graham displays beautiful court vision hitting Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk with a dime in the second half.
videos.headline: Kansas' Graham throws a bullet to Mykhailiuk
